{
  "name": "Gust",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-spiral-blue-gray.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You seize the air and compel it to create one of the following effects at a point you can see within range:</p><p><strong>Push:</strong> Choose another creature within Range. Make a Spell Check Contested by its Might Save, you are considered as Medium sized for the purposes of moving creatures with this Spell.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The target is pushed 1 Space horizontally in a direction of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> The target is pushed 1 additional Space.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Default spell behavior.</em></p><p><strong>Move Object:</strong> Choose one object that is neither held nor carried and that weighs less than 200 pounds (100 kg). Make a DC 15 Spell Check.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The object is pushed 1 Space horizontally in a direction of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The object is pushed up to 2 Spaces.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> up to 1 additional Space.</p></li></ul><p>This distance is increased by 2 Spaces if the object weights less than 50 Pounds (25 kg).</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Distance: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The target is pushed an additional 2 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Grand Gust: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Your size category for using Push increases by 1 (up to a maximum of Colossal) and the maximum weight you can affect with Move Object increases by 200 pounds (100 kg).</p><p><strong>Harsh Wind: (2 MP)</strong> On a Success, the target is also Blinded and Deafened for 1 round.</p>",
